<div class="container">
  <h1>About PDF Slayer</h1>
  <p><strong>PDF Slayer</strong> is a free, browser-based OCR (Optical Character Recognition) tool designed to help users extract editable text from PDF and image files instantly — with support for both English and Hindi languages.</p>

  <p>Our mission is to make document digitization easy and accessible for everyone, whether you’re a student, professional, or researcher. PDF Slayer runs entirely in your browser, meaning your files never leave your device. This ensures full <strong>privacy, security, and speed</strong>.</p>

  <h2 style="color:#ff4d4d;">Why Choose PDF Slayer?</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ Fast and secure local processing (no uploads)</li>
    <li>✅ Supports Hindi and English text extraction</li>
    <li>✅ Works on PDFs and common image formats (JPG, PNG, BMP)</li>
    <li>✅ 100% Free with no sign-up required</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 style="color:#ff4d4d;">Our Vision</h2>
  <p>We believe that powerful tools should be simple, secure, and free to use. PDF Slayer will continue improving its recognition accuracy and adding language support to make it useful for users across the world.</p>

